`treeFile::enumerateFiles`.
  Version 4â†’5, 98 names.
- **Ask B** â€” **provider-detected (Option P)**. Behavior-only fix: the in-world CUI reflow now 
keys off the
  **back-buffer** size (`Graphics::getFrameBufferMaxWidth/Height`) instead of the *current 
render-target*
  size, so it tracks back down to the embed panel after the fullscreen restyle. No contract change.
