**Status (2026-06-17):** 32-01 GATE PASS + 32-02 (D3DCompile/HlslRewrite/X4016-fix/bytecode-cache) 
COMPLETE & committed. The 32-bit cantina OOM is a D3DCompile-on-32-bit limit, **DEFERRED TO x64 â€” 
do NOT revert** (Kenny's call). Next session = **x64 milestone work**, not more 32-bit chasing.
**Mode:** `/gsd:execute-phase 32` interactive-inline; worktrees OFF, sequential, on `master`.
