Adventures, April 2006 Roadshow, House Packup reward, etc. See [PlatformFeatureBits.h](D:/Code/swg-cl
ient-v2/src/engine/shared/library/sharedGame/src/shared/core/PlatformFeatureBits.h:21).
- Startup maps feature bits into SKU bits for Base, JTL, Episode 3, and Trials of Obi-Wan, so the 
client expects up to `sku3` content, not just base/JTL. See [ClientMain.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/sr
c/game/client/application/SwgClient/src/win32/ClientMain.cpp:232) and [ClientMain.cpp](D:/Code/swg-cl
ient-v2/src/game/client/application/SwgClient/src/win32/ClientMain.cpp:263).
- UI code has Mustafar and Hoth loading mediators: [SwgCuiMediatorTypes.h](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/
game/client/library/swgClientUserInterface/src/shared/core/SwgCuiMediatorTypes.h:122), [SwgCuiMediato
rFactorySetup.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/game/client/library/swgClientUserInterface/src/shared/co
re/SwgCuiMediatorFactorySetup.cpp:272).
- Travel UI knows `mustafar` and `kashyyyk_main`: [SwgCuiTicketPurchase.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/sr
c/game/client/library/swgClientUserInterface/src/shared/page/SwgCuiTicketPurchase.cpp:732).

**Space contract:** the code is newer than a base-JTL UI dataset. `SwgCuiHudSpace` hard-fetches the 
space HUD buttons/widgets and specifically requires `buttonEnterSpace`, `missileLockOnYou`, and 
`missileLockOnYouDeformer`: [SwgCuiHudSpace.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/game/client/library/swgCli
entUserInterface/src/shared/page/SwgCuiHudSpace.cpp:119). The atmospheric flight button is not 
first-class wired here: it is fetched, immediately hidden, and `rg` finds no other references beyond 
the member/constructor. See [SwgCuiHudSpace.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/game/client/library/swgCli
entUserInterface/src/shared/page/SwgCuiHudSpace.cpp:129).

**Nebula contract:** lightning is real code, not vestigial. Nebula lightning requires a non-empty 
`getLightningAppearance()` and creates it through `AppearanceTemplateList::createAppearance()` as a 
`LightningAppearance`: [NebulaManagerClient.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clie
ntGame/src/shared/space/NebulaManagerClient.cpp:752), [NebulaManagerClient.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2
