and check one compatibility probe: does `/ui/ui_hud_space.inc` contain all 7 `SwgCuiHudSpace` 
CodeData mappings and widgets, and do the referenced nebula lightning appearance assets instantiate 
as `LightningAppearance`? If yes, the current operator paired a late-NGE source tree with 
older/incomplete JTL-ish data. If no even in a version-matched data set, it is a real SWGSource JTL 
support gap.
